title: Milo Ventimiglia

itunes:subtitle: Secure your oxygen masks, tighten the yellow straps, and breathe slowly because this week our guest is the man, the myth...Milo Ventimiglia (This is Us, Gilmore Girls, Heroes). Karen Sarducci calls a meeting with the man everyone in town is talking about
description:
Secure your oxygen masks, tighten the yellow straps, and breathe slowly because this week our guest is the man, the myth...Milo Ventimiglia (This is Us, Gilmore Girls, Heroes). Karen Sarducci calls a meeting with the man everyone in town is talking about and even gets her son Milo (played by Paul Scheer) on the phone so the two Milos can meet!  After some Unqualified dealbreakers, Anna, Sim, and Milo call Jenny, whose husband wants to get his PhD around the same time she wants to have kids.  They also give unqualified advice to Rachel, who doesn’t know what to do when a family she used to babysit for ropes her into the drama of an affair!

Hosted on Acast. See acast.com/privacy for more information.
